### GET: Retrieve an item by ID
GET http://localhost:80/api/item?id=99
Accept: application/json

### POST: Create a new item
POST http://localhost:80/api/item
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "New Item",
  "description": "A sample item."
}

### PUT: Update an existing item
PUT http://localhost:80/api/item?id=99
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Item",
  "description": "Updated description."
}

### PATCH: Partially update an item
PATCH http://localhost:80/api/item?id=99
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "description": "Partially updated description."
}

### DELETE: Remove an item
DELETE http://localhost:80/api/item?id=99
Accept: application/json

### POST: Upload a file
POST http://localhost:80/api/item/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json

file=@/path/to/example.txt
